title: Tekken 6 (Emulated for PC)
description:
This is a PSP emulation for PC using PPSSPP emulator.

Tested on Windows 7 32 & 64 bit OS.

The emulator has pre-configured controls for Xbox360 controller.

Game info:

Tekken 6 sees the return of many familiar faces as well as new characters to create the largest line-up the series has ever seen. Adding to the already rich gaming experience, a deeper character customization feature will only further enhance the incredible fighting intensity as players knuckle up against each others. Players can also take the battle online for classic match-ups and to compete for world domination.



                   Recommended System Requirements:

Core 2 duo 2.4ghz or higher.

nVidia GeForce GT 610 / ATI Radeon HD 5 series or higher.

2 Gig of ram or more.

Windows XP / Vista / 7 / 8 32 or 64bit OS.



                          Additional info:


Press Alt + Enter to toggle Window Modes.

Press Alt + F4 to end the game.

Best played using a gamepad, as playing with keyboard only can be awkward.
